Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.deeco.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    KMException
    KMException is the base class for the the Knowledge Manager related errors.
    KMIllegalArgumentException
    KMIllegalArgumentException is thrown whenever there is a type matching related problem, while retrieving knowledge.
    KMNotExistentException
    KMNotExistentException is thrown whenever the knowledge manager is unable to retreive required property in the knowledge structure.
    KnowledgeRepositoryException
    KnowledgeRepositoryException is thrown whenever there is a repository communication problem.
    SessionException
    SessionException is thrown whenever there is a session related problem.
    UnavailableEntryException
    UnavailableEntryException is thrown by the knowledge repository whenever the entry specified by the key is unavailable.
